### =========================================

### Sad/Melancholic - No voice cloning
POST {{baseUrl}}/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "I never thought it would end this way. After all these years, all we've been through together.",
  "system_prompt": "Generate audio following instruction.\n\n<|scene_desc_start|>\nA deeply sad and melancholic delivery. The speaker is reflecting on loss with a heavy heart. Voice should crack slightly with emotion, slow pace, long pauses between phrases.\n<|scene_desc_end|>"
}

